            <title>[LU-18616] kernel update [RHEL 9.5 5.14.0-503.21.1.el9_5]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18616</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: perf/aux: Fix AUX buffer serialization (CVE-2024-46713)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: RDMA/bnxt_re: Fix a bug while setting up Level-2 PBL pages (CVE-2024-50208)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: mlxsw: spectrum_ipip: Fix memory leak when changing remote IPv6 address (CVE-2024-50252)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: mptcp: cope racing subflow creation in mptcp_rcv_space_adjust (CVE-2024-53122)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


